\langle N,\nu_1\rangle = \cos\alpha 
\langle N,\nu_2\rangle = \cos\beta 
\cos (\alpha-\beta)=\cos\alpha\cos\beta+\sin \alpha\sin\beta
 \cos^2\alpha +\cos^2\beta - 2 \cos\alpha\cos\beta \cos (\alpha-\beta) = \sin^2(\alpha-\beta) \tag1
\begin{split} \cos^2\alpha + \cos^2\beta &- 2 \cos^2\alpha\cos^2\beta - 2\cos\alpha\cos\beta\sin \alpha\sin\beta \\ &=\cos^2\alpha(1-\cos^2\beta)+\cos^2\beta(1-\cos^2\alpha)-2\cos\alpha\cos\beta\sin \alpha\sin\beta  \\& = \cos^2\alpha\sin^2\beta+\cos^2\beta \sin^2\alpha -2\cos\alpha\cos\beta\sin \alpha\sin\beta   \\&=(\sin\alpha\cos\beta-\cos\alpha\sin\beta)^2 \\& = \sin^2(\alpha-\beta) \end{split}
